{"tid":1623740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(非風向）唔通你真係諗住人哋派兵過嚟幫你？","createTime":"2019-10-05T01:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T01:28:10.000Z","uid":288058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1d9c4e0eca4a22854175a01e35411bf68d6094e0","tid":1623740,"uid":288058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:22:03.000Z","msg":"以下純屬個人見解<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其實大家話冇咗國際戰線，失去美國支持<br />\n<br />\n講真唔通人哋真係出兵幫你打仗爭取重新貫徹一國兩制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n民主及人權法案只係美國頂多可以做嘅嘢，推動支共重新落實一國兩制<br />\n<br />\n但中共撚會聽你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國一直以嚟其實已經出晒面，而家話要臨時政府aka獨立，佢唔通又突然之間話支持你地咩（唔支持唔代表唔可以）咁樣嘅話支那又有藉口PLA到時對全世界情況都好不利<br />\n<br />\n香港人要靠自己，唔好成日依賴別人，點解我哋而家要好似成隻狗咁美國講乜我哋就要聽，雖則話人哋支持同埋某程度上幫你，但係使唔使掉轉槍頭屌返自己友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">重申一次唔撚係風向post啊屌你<br />\n意見不合就話人哋三毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"24044ef401e8be9d7db31ad68b092cb828b5171f","tid":1623740,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:22:43.000Z","msg":"［極重要］做嘢還做嘢，P牌仔想畀個革命方向大家討論討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1621742\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1621742</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5a7985e05f2f7f0152e1b802fb7905ec6b0b8b2c","tid":1623740,"uid":288058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:24:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">解散警隊 刻不容緩</span></span>"},{"pid":"2d120a56622094fdcb9ee978328727d9a63a215c","tid":1623740,"uid":288058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:24:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">驅逐共黨 光復香港</span></span>"},{"pid":"6